race.description: Sportsbet Set A Deposit Limit Handicap
race.comment: GOGOLF GURU (13) has been knocking on the door for a while and gets a terrific chance to break through. Maps to blend in beautifully from the middle draw over a track and trip she thrives on. In light again at the weights and clearly the one they have to beat. QUEENOFTHEAIR (12) improved last time without quite finding her top. The rise to the mile looks ideal and the blinkers going on for the first time should sharpen her. If she brings her best, she could put them away. CARING LASS (4) continues to leave herself with too much to do but is finding the line well. Drops slightly in grade and steps back in trip. Expect her to be launching late. DIDWEWIN (5) knuckled down bravely to score at Port Lincoln. This is tougher, but she's open to further improvement fourth-up and draws to get every favour from the inside. Must include. SHADOW HAWK (14) resumes short of his preferred trip and hasn't won for a long time, but his peaks measure up. Worth keeping safe in exotics to add some spice.
